These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Color: mauve, ebony, green
1. Color:ebony is on the right of Color:green##1
2. Color:mauve is on the far right##1
3. Color:mauve is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Color   | green | ebony | mauve |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Sport: ice-hockey, parkour, biathlon
1. Sport:parkour is in an odd position##4
2. Sport:ice-hockey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | biathlon | parkour |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Flower: daffodil, rose, begonia
1. Flower:rose is in an even position##4
2. Flower:rose is on the left or right of Flower:begonia##3
3. Flower:begonia is on the right of Flower:rose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Flower   | daffodil | rose | begonia |

 #################################
 
